            </h2>
        </header>
        <div id="mapModalBody" class="panel-body">
            <div class="modal-wrapper">
                <div class="modal-text">

                    <div id="googleMap" style="min-height:650px;" class=" col-centered panel-body "><span class="close">Close</span></div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
        <footer class="panel-footer">
            <div class="row">
                <div class="col-md-12 text-right">
                    <button class="btn btn-primary modal-confirm" id="map-cnf" onClick="history.go(0)" >Confirm</button>
                    <button class="btn btn-default modal-dismiss" onClick="history.go(0)">Cancel</button>
                </div>
